<l>ūṭa luṇartal puṇarta livaikāmaṅ </l>
<l>kūṭiyār peṟṟa payaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Love quarrel, reconciliation and intercourse - these are the advantages reaped by those who marry for lust.</l>
